{"type": "article", "id": 34211, "title": "这不是花灯，这真的是野餐篮｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-07T23:09:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3008, "name": "Ronan & Erwan Bouroullec"}, {"id": 34691, "name": "SUPERLIFE"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 34692, "name": "Corse Design Factory"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/201611072211254p5lEVOZNbx6B1Ci.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Chains by Ronan &amp; Erwan Bouroullec</h3><p>Ronan 和 Erwan Bouroullec 两兄弟组成的<a href=\"http://www.bouroullec.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">设计组合</a>最近带来了一款名为 <a href=\"http://www.bouroullec.com/view_projets_detail_new.php?id=296\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chains</a> 的灯饰，随性的组合叠加让人感受到了模块化设计的无限可能。它由一系列钟形灯罩组成，既有呈现金属感的铝制版，也有白色的石膏版和体现出光泽的红色陶瓷版。即使不开灯，它在空间内的存在感也非常抢眼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221154oKLJ6q8f3zQ5p709.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611072211549KPJhy2O6IMknVUl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.185819\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611072211553arGJF28lznDeMKb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.515892\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221155OcZSkP9Eqj17zHa8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676039\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LA Chair by ZAOZUO</h3><p>          </p><p>L 形的弧面椅背加上 A 形的扶手椅腿，<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">造作</a>旗下的设计师利用两个字母造型的组合打造了这把名副其实的<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300157\" rel=\"nofollow\">洛城椅</a>。自成一体的 L 形座椅由曲木制成，优雅的弧度相当自然地延伸至前端的缓坡。铁管弯折而成的椅腿采用了梯形结构，为搬运和堆叠提供了一定的便利。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221222szKQcmYG4HlF3W2n.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.408854\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611072212225gUBtv8PIAuMemiq.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221222or7l6wjfUgm0BSPk.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.408854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221221nVxUtXNgjrEPsfAO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Glouton by SUPERLIFE</h3><p>你会怎么处理那些打算重复利用的购物袋？如果你觉得把它们放在外面并不怎么好看，瑞典工作室 <a href=\"http://www.superlife.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SUPERLIFE</a> 带来的置物架 <a href=\"http://www.superlife.ch/#/works/glouton.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Glouton</a> 或许会让你省心不少。半圆形的架子有一道弹性织物带所组成“门帘”，需要时只要拨开它将塑料袋抽出来即可。如果是纸袋的话，可以折一折放进后半部分的矩形槽内。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221238emgMfGz3yuAiwvI9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221238EJ2SNitWuz4k3Dy7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221238w5odLNvG1nCrqJmy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221238J75y1GYqFOu3VBeP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Back to Nature by Andrea Mangone</h3><p>塑料垃圾有没有可能转变成对自然有益的产品？意大利设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/AndreamangoneID\" rel=\"nofollow\">Andrea Mangone</a> 为此构想了一套名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/44183437/BACK-TO-NATURE-recycled-plastic\" rel=\"nofollow\">Back to Nature</a> 的产品。这个系列包括了蜂巢、花盆和一个喂鸟器，它们全都由回收来的塑料制品加工而成。在这套产品中，蜂巢和喂鸟器的主体以及花盆都是采用更坚固的高密度聚乙烯塑料制品制作而成的，塑料袋等低密度聚乙烯塑料制品则被用来制作蜂巢和喂鸟器的吊绳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221306eIQB60kSYnf3WxyR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523571\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221302bePVZpljrtk2CfMD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221303Dxd3Yru6jHvBUmky.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221302nwPDAxBKMXoq30iO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Picnic Basket by Corse Design Factory</h3><p>设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.corse.nyc/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Corse Design Factory</a> 每年都会进行一个慈善项目，今年设计师们为美国长岛的儿童慈善机构 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ronald_McDonald_House_Charities\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ronald McDonald House</a> 所举办的 Project Picnic 活动打造了一套造型非常别致的<a href=\"http://www.corse.nyc/works/project-picnic-2016-basket\" rel=\"nofollow\">野餐用品</a>。其中最吸引人眼球的就是以日本薬玉为灵感所设计的球形野餐篮，薬玉是一种装饰性质的香包，有时会用纸制作，还会同纸灯一起出现。非常规的野餐篮造型加上黑白橙的颜色搭配看起来相当上镜，配套的两个长筒则是参考了纸灯所设计的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221352S0eT1cwChb7uPaNX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221352wjLixm9VuvNSFIM8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221353qy5aGXOV3BvlLW28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221353CsTMbn5DvUqthzA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Luxury Chocolate Series by Maria Le Quang</h3><p class=\"\">如果你喜欢渐变色，德国设计学生 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/marialequang\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maria Le Quang</a> 带来的这套巧克力概念包装会让你感受到彩虹的甜美。这些看似随性的颜色搭配其实都是配合了“粉色香槟”、“极地盐”这些口味挑选而出的，激发人们对这些前所未闻的味道进行想象。包装正反的标签也延续了二元渐变色的简洁风格，由巧克力名构成的圆圈内标注了可可含量，略大一号的字体直截了当地传递出了基本信息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110722140932LYeUXbsAZg5zwS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221408uRFM9xkY1W7Il4DX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.626000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221408Rx36pKNhuvtwQFWc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221408DjlTzn5pLC6yMe7Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161107221408nuhSW64VwMA19XJD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}